Notebook[{

Cell[CellGroupData[{
Cell["Neural networks - Part II", "Chapter",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.782050144796915*^9, 3.7820501521734066`*^9}, {
  3.8149629578252916`*^9, 
  3.8149629595057487`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"8e1d7f66-8b10-41d3-acea-\
a4deb4a6f841"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "In part I, we have seen how to build very simple ANNs and how to extract \
information form ANNs. We also saw how to use ",
 StyleBox["Classify", "CodeText"],
 " and ",
 StyleBox["Predict", "CodeText"],
 " functions to automatically build and train ANNs for classification and \
prediction problems.\n\nThe aims of this part are:"
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.7821094203286314`*^9, 
  3.782109517885336*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"ad43e0d8-0f83-4abd-8685-\
f56b55ecacc9"],

Cell["\<\
To introduce the structure of data for ANNs: Tensors, net encoders, net \
decoders\
\>", "Item",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.782109526231251*^9, 3.782109536391286*^9}, 
   3.7821096611544685`*^9, {3.78218517025027*^9, 3.7821851845708313`*^9}, {
   3.7821852331028824`*^9, 3.7821852511311207`*^9}, {3.7821858486475954`*^9, 
   3.782185860894884*^9}, {3.7821921705442305`*^9, 
   3.782192189457212*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"46dfc950-f92f-4b3f-80bd-\
dae4769e1795"],

Cell["To explore some pre-trained models.", "Item",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.782109526231251*^9, 3.782109536391286*^9}, 
   3.7821096611544685`*^9},ExpressionUUID->"d759c7b9-a3b0-43ca-a317-\
188b876f3505"],

Cell["To evaluate the accuracy of trained ANNs using test data.", "Item",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.782109526231251*^9, 
  3.7821095617134905`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"24b8af10-b8ce-41f6-9cb5-\
6f8159b3a1fd"],

Cell["\<\
To describe net surgery and give an example where net surgery is applied (in \
a separate notebook, Ch8-3_ML_NeuralNetworks_NetSurgery.nb .\
\>", "Item",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.782109526231251*^9, 3.782109655577382*^9}, {
  3.8149630129315224`*^9, 3.8149630339755383`*^9}, {3.8259441873835225`*^9, 
  3.825944196411451*^9}, {3.8259455468004293`*^9, 
  3.8259455878334074`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"82b22445-c6fb-4f10-bc9c-\
b224c94fed2a"],

